B

BangBangController - Class in storm2013.utilities
The BangBangController has three parts: When the speed of the motor (found through the IEncoderSpeed interface which just gives the controller the motor speed in RPM) is less than BangBangController._spinUpPoint, the PIDOutput will be set to BangBangController._spinUpSpeed.
BangBangController(PIDOutput, IEncoderSpeed, ITable, double, double, double, double, double) - Constructor for class storm2013.utilities.BangBangController
The default (and only, at the moment) constructor.
